Interval estimation data reported in Vuorre & Metcalfe (2017)

Interval estimation data reported in Vuorre & Metcalfe (2017)

data(ie)

Format

A data frame (tibble::tibble) with 3011 rows and 5 variables:

id

ID of study participant.

condition

Experimental condition.

interval

Inter-stimulus interval.

estimate

Numerical duration estimate (participant's response).

cond

Dummy coded condition, 0=involuntary, 1=voluntary.

Source

Vuorre, M. & Metcalfe, J., (2017). Voluntary action alters the perception of visual illusions. Attention, Perception, & Psychophysics https://doi.org/10.3758/s13414-017-1321-x
